14
00:00:41,733 --> 00:00:46,266
in the first ever
    industrialized war.

15
00:00:46,266 --> 00:00:50,233
Nine million died as new
    and more powerful weapons

16
00:00:50,233 --> 00:00:52,333
enabled both sides
    to fight each other

17
