(artillery fire)

20
00:01:00,266 --> 00:01:02,133
(explosion)

21
00:01:02,133 --> 00:01:04,666
It was a war
    that came to epitomize

22
00:01:04,666 --> 00:01:07,600
man's inhumanity to man.

23
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:10,233
MAN:
    It must be a gas shell.

24
00:01:10,233 --> 00:01:12,600
MAN:
    Phosgene is not an instant gas.

25
00:01:12,600 --> 00:01:15,266
It can take 24 hours
    to come into effect.

26
00:01:15,266 --> 00:01:16,233
A horrible, horrible,

27
00:01:16,233 --> 00:01:18,500
and painful,
    agonizing way to die.

28
00:01:21,733 --> 00:01:23,033
NARRATOR:
    The dig is on a site

29
00:01:23,033 --> 00:01:25,100
where the entire history
    of that war

30
00:01:25,100 --> 00:01:29,600
is uniquely captured.

31
